### Key directories

```
src/
├── api/          # REST API routes
├── services/     # Business logic
├── models/       # Data models and database
├── middleware/    # Express middleware (auth, logging, error handling)
├── utils/        # Shared utilities
└── types/        # TypeScript type definitions
```

