## Team workflow

This project uses the Team SDLC skill. See `.team/config.yaml` for methodology settings and `.team/CONVENTIONS.md` for PR and commit conventions.

Branch policy: feature branches off `main`. No direct commits to `main`. PRs require review and CI checks.
